<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5008208>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Microcancilla phoenix sp.nov.(A) Holotype,MNRJ60299 (2.85 mm long).(B-H) Paratype,MNRJ 28183 (4.25 mm long).(A-B) entire shell in ventral view. (C) same, lateral view. (D) same, dorsal view, white square enlarged in E. (E) Detail of teleoconch sculpture, white square enlarged in F. (F) Detail of microscopic pustules covering the shell.(G) Protoconch in frontal view.(H) Protoconch in apical view.Scale bars:A-D = 1 mm;E,G,H = 100 µm;F = 20µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5008208/files/figure.png" .

